Call OUVRE_TRACE ("FQ79733: Designations CFG") From LECFIC
Local File ADOSSIER
Read [F:ADS]DOSSIER=nomap

Call DES2AXX([F:ADS]DOSSIER) From STOMAJ30

Call FERME_TRACE From LECFIC
Call LEC_TRACE From LECFIC
End



